---
// RoadmapSection.astro
// The "why tokiGig" section — competitive positioning + tokiOS trust layer + roadmap tease
// Operator language throughout — no tech jargon, no framework terms
// Structure:
//   1. Tension headline — most AI tools require assembly
//   2. 4 product-level advantages (why we win)
//   3. tokiOS trust layer (why you can trust it)
//   4. Product roadmap tease (more is coming)
---

<section class="home-section roadmap-section">

  <!-- ── Section intro — name the tension without naming competitors ──────── -->
  <div class="section-intro">
    <p class="route-kicker">Why tokiGig</p>
    <h2>Most AI tools require setup, configuration, and ongoing maintenance.</h2>
    <p>
      We built tokiGig for the business owner who doesn't have an engineering team —
      and doesn't want one just to run AI. No wiring. No stack. Just results.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 4 product advantages ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <!-- Operator-facing language — no mention of frameworks or pipelines     -->
  <div class="advantage-grid">

    <!-- 1. Operator-ready -->
    <div class="advantage-card">
      <div class="advantage-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Checkmark in a circle — "works out of the box" -->
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none">
          <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="12" stroke="var(--toki-green)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.5"/>
          <path d="M9 14.5L12.5 18L19 11" stroke="var(--toki-green-lt)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Operator-ready, not build-your-own</h3>
      <p>Works out of the box. No wiring agents. No configuring flows. No maintaining a stack. You run your business — we handle the AI.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. Understands your business -->
    <div class="advantage-card">
      <div class="advantage-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Magnifying glass with a dot — "sees your business" -->
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8" stroke="var(--toki-green)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" fill="var(--toki-green-lt)" opacity="0.8"/>
          <line x1="18" y1="18" x2="23" y2="23" stroke="var(--toki-green-lt)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Understands your business, not just your tools</h3>
      <p>Other tools connect apps. tokiGig interprets what you sell, maps how AI systems see you, and surfaces the gaps hurting your visibility and trust.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. Trust-native -->
    <div class="advantage-card">
      <div class="advantage-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Shield with line through center — "stays under control" -->
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none">
          <path d="M14 3L24 7.5V15C24 20.5 18.5 24.5 14 26C9.5 24.5 4 20.5 4 15V7.5Z" stroke="var(--toki-green)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
          <path d="M9.5 14.5L12.5 17.5L18.5 11.5" stroke="var(--toki-green-lt)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Trust-native by design</h3>
      <p>No silent automation. No black-box decisions. Every action is visible, every boundary is yours to set. AI that won't act without you.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. Built for outcomes -->
    <div class="advantage-card">
      <div class="advantage-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Arrow hitting target — "results not experiments" -->
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none">
          <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="11" stroke="var(--toki-green)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.3"/>
          <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="6"  stroke="var(--toki-green)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="2.5" fill="var(--toki-green-lt)"/>
          <line x1="14" y1="14" x2="25" y2="3" stroke="var(--toki-green-lt)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Built for outcomes, not experiments</h3>
      <p>Not a playground. Improve your AI visibility, increase trust signals, and make your business show up when AI recommends services in your category.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ── tokiOS trust layer ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <!-- Why you can trust it — operator translation of technical capabilities -->
  <div class="tokios-band">

    <div class="tokios-band__intro">
      <!-- One anchor sentence — leads with trust not technology -->
      <p class="tokios-band__kicker">Powered by tokiOS</p>
      <h3>An AI system designed to be visible, reliable, and under your control.</h3>
      <p>
        tokiOS is the engine behind every tokiGig tool. You don't need to know how it works —
        you just need to know you can trust it. Here's why.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="tokios-pillars">

      <!-- Auditable -->
      <div class="tokios-pillar">
        <span class="tokios-pillar__label">Auditable</span>
        <p>Every action is visible. If something changes in your business, you'll know why — not after the fact, but in real time.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Guardrails -->
      <div class="tokios-pillar">
        <span class="tokios-pillar__label">Guardrails</span>
        <p>You define the boundaries. AI won't do anything you didn't approve. No surprise behavior. No going rogue.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Reliable -->
      <div class="tokios-pillar">
        <span class="tokios-pillar__label">Reliable</span>
        <p>Built like infrastructure, not a demo. It works the same way every time — you can depend on it like you depend on your CRM.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust-building -->
      <div class="tokios-pillar">
        <span class="tokios-pillar__label">Trust-building</span>
        <p>The more you use it, the more you trust it. Starts transparent. Stays accountable. Improves with your oversight over time.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- tokiOS link — subtle, not a hard sell -->
    <p class="tokios-band__foot">
      <a href="/os">Learn more about tokiOS →</a>
    </p>

  </div>

  <!-- ── Product roadmap tease ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <!-- Shows trajectory — tokiScan is live, more is coming                  -->
  <div class="roadmap-tease">

    <p class="roadmap-tease__label">The platform</p>
    <p class="roadmap-tease__sub">tokiScan is live. More is coming.</p>

    <div class="module-list" aria-label="tokiGig platform modules">

      <!-- tokiScan — live -->
      <article class="module-row module-row--active">
        <div>
          <h3>tokiScan</h3>
          <p>AI visibility diagnostic</p>
        </div>
        <span class="module-badge module-badge--live">Available now</span>
      </article>

      <!-- tokiPatch — coming -->
      <article class="module-row">
        <div>
          <h3>tokiPatch</h3>
          <p>Closes the gaps tokiScan finds — automatically</p>
        </div>
        <span class="module-badge">Coming soon</span>
      </article>

      <!-- tokiWorker — coming -->
      <article class="module-row">
        <div>
          <h3>tokiWorker</h3>
          <p>Autonomous AI workforce — runs without babysitting</p>
        </div>
        <span class="module-badge">Coming soon</span>
      </article>

      <!-- Placeholder — signals there's even more in the pipeline -->
      <article class="module-row module-row--ghost">
        <div>
          <h3>More tools in development</h3>
          <p>We're building the full operator stack — visibility, fixes, automation, and beyond</p>
        </div>
        <span class="module-badge">In the lab</span>
      </article>
        </div>

        <!-- ── Developer / nerd nod — one line, tucked under the roadmap ─────── -->
        <!-- Intentionally subtle — this is for the curious, not the casual visitor -->
    <div class="dev-nod">
        <a href="https://discord.gg/7Dj56T34VZ" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="dev-nod__link">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Discord logo path -->
        <path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057c.002.022.015.043.033.055a19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03zM8.02 15.33c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.956-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.956 2.418-2.157 2.418zm7.975 0c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.955-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.946 2.418-2.157 2.418z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Follow the build — join our Discord</span>
        </a>
        <p>
        Watch what we're shipping. Get early access to new tools. Tell us what your business actually needs.
        Operators, developers, and curious nerds all welcome.
         </p>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<style>
  /* ── Advantage grid — 2x2 on desktop, 1 col on mobile ────────────────── */
  .advantage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Individual advantage card — same token pattern as pillar cards */
  .advantage-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-base);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .advantage-card__icon {
    /* Icon sized and glowed — matches pillar section treatment */
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px var(--toki-green-glow));
    transition: filter 0.3s ease;
  }

  .advantage-card:hover .advantage-card__icon {
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(122, 184, 106, 0.6));
  }

  .advantage-card h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .advantage-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── tokiOS trust band ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .tokios-band {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    /* Subtle green tint — distinct from plain cards, signals the OS layer */
    border: 1px solid var(--border-green);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
  }

  .tokios-band__intro {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  /* Kicker label */
  .tokios-band__kicker {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--toki-green);
  }

  .tokios-band__intro h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 24px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .tokios-band__intro p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* 4 pillars in a row — stack to 2 col on mobile */
  .tokios-pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-base);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Individual pillar */
  .tokios-pillar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Pillar label — green pill */
  .tokios-pillar__label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--toki-green);
    background: rgba(90, 143, 78, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-green);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .tokios-pillar p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* tokiOS footer link */
  .tokios-band__foot {
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-base);
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .tokios-band__foot a {
    color: var(--toki-green-lt);
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .tokios-band__foot a:hover {
    color: var(--toki-green);
  }

  /* ── Roadmap tease ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .roadmap-tease {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .roadmap-tease__label {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--toki-green);
  }

  .roadmap-tease__sub {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* Live badge — green pill */
  .module-badge {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .module-badge--live {
    color: var(--toki-green);
    background: rgba(90, 143, 78, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-green);
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  /* Ghost row — "more in the lab" — more muted than coming soon rows */
  .module-row--ghost {
    opacity: 0.5;
    border-style: dashed;
  }

  /* ── Developer nod — subtle, tucked under roadmap ────────────────────── */
.dev-nod {
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  /* Dashed border — visually connects to the ghost row above it */
  border: 1px dashed var(--border-strong);
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

/* Discord link row */
.dev-nod__link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  transition: color 0.15s;
}

/* Discord purple on hover — only place on the site, earns it */
.dev-nod__link:hover {
  color: #7289da;
}

.dev-nod__link svg {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  opacity: 0.7;
  transition: opacity 0.15s;
}

.dev-nod__link:hover svg {
  opacity: 1;
}

.dev-nod p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

  /* ── Responsive ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    /* Advantage grid goes 1 col */
    .advantage-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    /* tokiOS pillars go 2 col */
    .tokios-pillars {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    /* tokiOS pillars go 1 col on small screens */
    .tokios-pillars {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>